Outline

Methods:

  Beginning of program: Prompt user if they are buyer or seller.
    If Buyer, input wallet and options available are
      print catalog 
      print catagory by price cap
      add to shopping cart & removes item
      delete from shopping cart
      check out
      search item
      Print out wallet amount
    If Seller,
      print catalog
      add item
      remove item
      search item
  Catalog - Hashtable with array of catalogs and chain of items
  Hashfunction - defined by the catagories
  Item Structure - Name, Catagory, Price
  Shopping Cart - Linked list
  
Catagories:
Sports
Men's Clothing
Women's Clothing
Electronics
Food
Movies
Games
Books
Arts and Crafts
Health and Beauty
